                     <interp inst="t17890603-73-off354" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890603-73-off354" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, sixty pounds weight of bacon, value 30 s. an iron hook, value 2 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17890603-73-victim727" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Hawkes
                  <interp inst="t17890603-73-victim727" type="surname" value="Hawkes"></interp>
