                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890603-73-defend725 t17890603-73-punish359"></join>
               imprisoned six months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
